		      To subscribe, go <a 
    		  href="http://lists.infradead.org/mailman/listinfo/linux-mtd-cvs/">
					here</a>
	    	</p> 	
		<p><b>NOTE:</b><br /> This list is read only. Do not post to this list!</p>
	</li>
	</ul>
